  "title": "Mechanical Design Engineer (Machine Design)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Drive the design of next-generation semiconductor automation equipment and modules, transforming ideas into functional designs and prototypes.</li>\n  <li>Create detailed fabrication, assembly, and layout drawings using 3D CAD tools, such as <a href=\"https://www.google.com/search?sca_esv=27e57b1e925aecdc&amp;cs=0&amp;sxsrf=AE3TifMzZ13w-EGRY3r1FwKsp0dnYsrcgQ%3A1760062925677&amp;q=CREO&amp;sa=X&amp;ved=2ahUKEwi9sLiryZiQAxUrRmwGHVvsONMQxccNegQIGhAB&amp;mstk=AUtExfBD8I6tQb82Uhz2MIsWEXL0SvxsLoz3Suw1anVznPlNYXyVtl7pmZQ4Pn827z4cDMyHLsYMFeZH_Tz5tQeLOea0hBD_1ogmzTco9R0EwArLB4oa-83eOobZYJvNIkqoKfnC26a-rP06BIa5rXYWzycqdXdZhDD4PUTPVXsA2FT7mbPiaxPOcvkga9QcAz7XEQKjnP1KifEIov_Wwwh-ax6JI1jEboWAwlpAohj2-jTnPDgvNQ_LBtCsSxIquK3pKfopo_wGNZ1W9zmusKBvbXP1&amp;csui=3\">CREO</a>, <a href=\"https://www.google.com/search?sca_esv=27e57b1e925aecdc&amp;cs=0&amp;sxsrf=AE3TifMzZ13w-EGRY3r1FwKsp0dnYsrcgQ%3A1760062925677&amp;q=SolidWorks&amp;sa=X&amp;ved=2ahUKEwi9sLiryZiQAxUrRmwGHVvsONMQxccNegQIGhAC&amp;mstk=AUtExfBD8I6tQb82Uhz2MIsWEXL0SvxsLoz3Suw1anVznPlNYXyVtl7pmZQ4Pn827z4cDMyHLsYMFeZH_Tz5tQeLOea0hBD_1ogmzTco9R0EwArLB4oa-83eOobZYJvNIkqoKfnC26a-rP06BIa5rXYWzycqdXdZhDD4PUTPVXsA2FT7mbPiaxPOcvkga9QcAz7XEQKjnP1KifEIov_Wwwh-ax6JI1jEboWAwlpAohj2-jTnPDgvNQ_LBtCsSxIquK3pKfopo_wGNZ1W9zmusKBvbXP1&amp;csui=3\">SolidWorks</a>, or other acceptable software.</li>\n  <li>Perform structural, kinematic, and dynamic analyses, including <a href=\"https://www.google.com/search?sca_esv=27e57b1e925aecdc&amp;cs=0&amp;sxsrf=AE3TifMzZ13w-EGRY3r1FwKsp0dnYsrcgQ%3A1760062925677&amp;q=Finite+Element+Analysis+%28FEA%29&amp;sa=X&amp;ved=2ahUKEwi9sLiryZiQAxUrRmwGHVvsONMQxccNegQIIxAB&amp;mstk=AUtExfBD8I6tQb82Uhz2MIsWEXL0SvxsLoz3Suw1anVznPlNYXyVtl7pmZQ4Pn827z4cDMyHLsYMFeZH_Tz5tQeLOea0hBD_1ogmzTco9R0EwArLB4oa-83eOobZYJvNIkqoKfnC26a-rP06BIa5rXYWzycqdXdZhDD4PUTPVXsA2FT7mbPiaxPOcvkga9QcAz7XEQKjnP1KifEIov_Wwwh-ax6JI1jEboWAwlpAohj2-jTnPDgvNQ_LBtCsSxIquK3pKfopo_wGNZ1W9zmusKBvbXP1&amp;csui=3\">Finite Element Analysis (FEA)</a> simulations and tolerance stack-ups, to ensure design robustness.</li>\n  <li>Work with software, electronics, and vision engineering teams to integrate mechanical designs into complete system solutions.</li>\n  <li>Apply Design for Manufacturing (DFM), Design for Assembly (DFA), and concurrent engineering principles to ensure efficient and robust designs.</li>\n  <li>Develop and validate pneumatic and hydraulic circuits and ultra-precision, high-speed pick-and-place mechanisms.</li>\n  <li>Contribute to design standardization, cost optimization, and project management for research and development initiatives.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Job Requirement:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Minimum Degree in Mechanical Engineering or related field</li>\n  <li>Minimum 5 year working experience in Mechanical Design in Automation/ Semiconductor Industry</li>\n</ul>\n<p>To submit your application, please apply online to <a href=\"mailto:apply@rn-care.com\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>apply@rn-care.com </strong></a>or call +(65) <a href=\"tel:6513 5697\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>6513 5697</strong></a> for private and confidential discussion.</p>\n<p>Your interest will be treated with the strictest of confidence. We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified or contacted.</p>\n<p><strong>RN Care Pte. Ltd</strong><br>\n<strong>EA License No: 17C8900</strong></p>",
